-- Turkey's Garanti Bank to secure funding worth up to $750 million
-- By Ece Toksabay
-- Mon May 12, 2014 10:45AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, May 12 (Reuters) - Turkish lender Garanti Bank <GARAN.IS> said on Monday it mandated its head office to secure funding worth up to $750 million with a maximum term of 15 years.

